"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-10-paris-2024-olympics-sports-minister-apologises-to-nigerians-after-disastrous-outing\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published on By The Minister of Sports Development, John Enoh, has apologised to Nigerians following Team Nigeria's disappointing outing at the 2024 Paris Olympics, where the country did not secure any medals.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997738764506, \"rank\": 2.26123458959269e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Minister\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports Development\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 50}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 163}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"any medals\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DAILY POST reports that Nigeria officially finished its outing at the 2024 Olympics in Paris, France, without winning a single medal.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.344971336788239e-17, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997738764506, \"rank\": 2.26123458959269e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999951064638, \"rank\": 4.89368333960592e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998974954367269, \"rank\": 6.137798451859597e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its outing\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"a single medal\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hannah Reuben was the last athlete left to salvage a medal for Nigeria on Saturday but she lost her second-round fight in the women's freestyle wrestling 76kg, losing 5-2 (victory by points) to Mongolia's Davaanasan Amar Enkh.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997738764506, \"rank\": 2.26123458959269e-07, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.984459530895558, \"rank\": 0.01577009669284103, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hannah Reuben\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"the last athlete\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"her second-round fight\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's freestyle wrestling\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement he personally signed on Saturday, Enoh said: \\\"The Olympic Games, Paris 2024, have ended, and I accept that our performance should have been a lot better.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"Enoh\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It obviously fell short of our objectives, expectations, and hopes of Nigerians.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our objectives\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"hopes\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I must apologise to our compatriots and reflect on what went wrong while looking forward to the Paralympic Games, Paris 2024 (August 28-September 8th).\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our compatriots\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"September 8th\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I assumed office as the Minister of Sports Development in August 2023, I was confronted with the task of executing four international competitions, namely the AFCON, the African Games, and the Olympic and Paralympic Games, in a matter of a few months.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"office\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the Minister\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports Development\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"four international competitions\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"namely the AFCON\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the African Games\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a few months\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was also reminded that the Olympic Games is the world's supreme sports competition, and countries require at least four years to prepare for it.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's supreme sports competition\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"at least four years\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I held extensive discussions with the management staff of the Ministry and got to know that preparations for the Olympics, which was less than a year away, had not started.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extensive discussions\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the management staff\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ministry\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the true Nigerian spirit, it was our view that we should spare no effort to sustain the international sports image of our country.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999986504626588, \"rank\": 1.1561168093606191e-06, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our view\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"no effort\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"the international sports image\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our target was to re-enact the Atlanta 1996 performance or even improve on it.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.8555652787124174, \"rank\": 0.16881788549295598, \"text\": \"Atlanta 1996\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our target\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To this end, we embarked on a progressive approach to drive forward the performance of our athletes and coaches.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this end\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a progressive approach\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my first week in office, I requested all National Sports Federations furnish me with plans and programmes.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first week\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"office\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"all National Sports Federations\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"programmes\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also embarked on a nationwide inspection of our sports facilities.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nationwide inspection\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"our sports facilities\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In all these, the President and Commander in Chief of the Federation, HE Bola Ahmed Tinubu, ensured that funds were not a limiting factor.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bola_Tinubu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bola Ahmed Tinubu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bola_Tinubu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bola_Tinubu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"Commander\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"Chief\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Federation\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"funds\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"a limiting factor\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes' competition requirements were provided, allowances were paid early, and training grants were disbursed to all athletes.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes' competition requirements\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"allowances\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"training grants\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I made myself readily available to deal with any issue throughout the competition.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any issue\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, the underwhelming performance of our team is puzzling.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the underwhelming performance\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We owe Nigerians an explanation.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nigerians\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"an explanation\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There must be a lot of lessons to learn from our performance and improvements must be made in all ramifications.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"lessons\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"improvements\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"all ramifications\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time we returned from the Olympics without a medal was in 2012.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last time\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next two Olympics after that, we had a bronze medal in 2016 and a silver and bronze in the 2020 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2785}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a country, we deserve more.\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us turn the disastrous outcome of the 2024 Olympics into a huge positive for Nigerian sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999986504626588, \"rank\": 1.1561168093606191e-06, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"the disastrous outcome\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge positive\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scotland: Dessers scores in Rangers' home win against Motherwell Transfer: I want to leave - Osimhen tells Napoli U17 WWC: Sports Minister celebrates Nigeria's Flamingos for hammering Ecuado